name: Amundi Multi-Asset Portfolio UCITS ETF Dist
description_en: The Amundi Multi-Asset Portfolio UCITS ETF Dist is an actively managed ETF. The umbrella fund Amundi Multi-Asset Portfolio invests in various ETFs.
